          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "10292",
      "label": "7",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do ONE of the following special-interest options:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "10293",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "element",
              "tag": "strong",
              "attrs": {},
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Option A—Model Railroading."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " With your parent or guardian's and counselor's approval, do TWO of the following:"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10295",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Draw a layout of your own model railroad or one that could be built in your home. Design a point-to-point track or loop with different routings. Include one of the following: turnaround or terminal or yard or siding."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10296",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Build one model railroad car kit or one locomotive kit."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10297",
          "label": "3",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Name the scale of four popular model railroad gauges. Identify the scale of four model cars or locomotives."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10298",
          "label": "4",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Locate the website of four model railroad - related manufacturers or magazine publishers. Print information on their products and services and discuss the information with your counselor."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10299",
          "label": "5",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Build one railroad structure (from scratch or using a kit), paint and weather the structure, mount it on your layout or diorama, and make the surrounding area on the diorama scenic."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10300",
          "label": "6",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Alone or with others, build a model railroad or modular layout including ballast and scenery. Make electrical connections and operate a train. Describe what you enjoyed most."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10301",
          "label": "7",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Participate in a switching contest on a timesaver layout and record your time."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10294",
          "label": "8",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Explain the difference between powering and controlling a model railroad by using direct current, and powering and controlling a model railroad using digital command control."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10302",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "element",
              "tag": "strong",
              "attrs": {},
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Option B—Railfanning."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " With your parent or guardian's and counselor's approval, do TWO of the following:"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10303",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Visit a railroad museum, historical display, or a prototype railroad sponsored public event. With permission, photograph, digitally record, or sketch items of interest. Explain what you saw and describe your photos, sketches, or video."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10304",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Purchase tickets and ride a scenic or historic railroad. Under supervision, photograph the equipment and discuss with your counselor the historic significance of the operation."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10305",
          "label": "3",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Locate the website of four rail historical groups, then find information on the history of the rail preservation operations and purpose of each group. Talk with a member of one of the groups and find out how you might help."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "10306",
          "label": "4",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Plan a trip by rail between two points. Obtain a schedule and explain when the train should arrive at two intermediate points. Purchase the tickets and make the trip. Explain to your counselor what you saw."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}